    "topic": "Mobitz II block management",
    "stem": "A 72-year-old man reports episodic dizziness. ECG shows a fixed PR interval with intermittent non-conducted P waves and no progressive PR prolongation before the dropped beats. Which of the following is the most appropriate next step in management?",
