    "topic": "Post-MI papillary muscle rupture",
    "stem": "Three days after an inferior STEMI, a 66-year-old man develops acute dyspnea and a new holosystolic murmur at the apex, along with pulmonary edema and hypotension. Which of the following is the most likely cause of his new murmur?",
