    "stem": "A 6-year-old boy is brought to the emergency department after taking an unknown quantity of an over-the-counter cold and allergy medication. He is confused and agitated. Exam shows flushed, hot, dry skin and dilated pupils. Which of the following is the most likely causative agent?",
